==Film==
The finding of the sapling is not seen in Peter Jackson's ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King]]'' (2003). However, in the film we momentarily see a single blossom of "hope" on the previously dead tree during the Siege of [[Gondor]] and the imminent arrival of [[Aragorn]] on the Black Ships. At the time of the crowning of Aragorn the previously dead tree has returned to life and is in full blossom.
